《'''人物'''》（{{lang-en|''People''}}，原名：{{lang|en|''People Weekly''}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一本[[名流|名流]]及[[人性化故事|人性化故事]]的[[雜誌|雜誌]]，自1974年創刊，由{{le|梅瑞迪斯集團|Meredith Corporation}}印刷<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.adweek.com/digital/heres-what-meredith-is-doing-with-some-of-the-time-inc-titles-it-inherited/|title=Here's What Meredith Is Doing With Some of the Time Inc. Titles It Inherited|first=Sara|last=Jerde|date=June 12, 2018|accessdate=January 16, 2019|work=[[Adweek|Adweek]]|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020124727/https://www.adweek.com/digital/heres-what-meredith-is-doing-with-some-of-the-time-inc-titles-it-inherited/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《人物》擁有4,660萬名成年讀者群，是美國雜誌中最大讀者群的雜誌<ref>{{cite news|title=AARP Shows Largest Growth in Readership|first=Chandra|last=Johnston-Greene|url=http://www.foliomag.com/2009/aarp-shows-largest-readership-growth-people-largest-audience|newspaper=Folio Magazine|date=May 18, 2009|accessdate=September 9, 2012|archive-date=2016-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729215737/http://www.foliomag.com/2009/aarp-shows-largest-readership-growth-people-largest-audience/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2011年，《人物》的廣告收入為$9.97億美元，是美國雜誌中最高的廣告收入<ref>{{cite news|title=Magazines eke out gains in 2011|first=Matthew|last=Flamm|url=http://www.crainsnewyork.com/article/20120110/MEDIA_ENTERTAINMENT/120119987|newspaper=[[Crain's_New_York_Business|Crain's New York Business]]|date=January 10, 2012|accessdate=September 9, 2012|archive-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913090601/https://www.crainsnewyork.com/article/20120110/ENTERTAINMENT/120119987/magazines-eke-out-gains-in-2011|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006年，它的發行量為375萬，收入預計超過15億美元<ref name="variety">[http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117946434?categoryid=18&cs=1&s=h&p=0 People who need people] {{Wayback|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117946434?categoryid=18&cs=1&s=h&p=0 |date=20121026094328 }}, a July 2006 article from ''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]'' magazine.</ref>。由於其在編輯、發行及廣告方面的卓越表現，該雜誌於2005年10月被《[[廣告時代|廣告時代]]》評為「年度雜誌」<ref name="twp">[http://www.timewarner.com/corp/newsroom/pr/0,20812,1145648,00.html Martha Nelson Named Editor, The People Group] {{Wayback|url=http://www.timewarner.com/corp/newsroom/pr/0,20812,1145648,00.html |date=20110105133443 }}, a January 2006 [[Time_Warner|Time Warner]] press release.</ref>。2006年10月，《人物》於《廣告時代》的「年度A名單」中排名第六，並於{{le|Adweek|Adweek}}的「品牌開拓者名單」中排名第3位。

該雜誌刊登了大約50/50的名人和人類感興趣的文章。《人物》的編輯們聲稱不要製作純名人八卦，這足以帶領名人宣傳人員為該雜誌提出獨家建議，以及所謂的「公關友好戰略」<ref name="variety" />。

《人物》杂志最初的创办宗旨就是讲述平凡人的不凡故事，但除了报导普通人，也报导明星，每期杂志的封面-{人物}-都是读者希望获得更多了解的人。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/people-magazine-20091021-65238907.html |title=美国《人物》杂志创刊35周年 |access-date=2009-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110415005050/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/people-magazine-20091021-65238907.html |archive-date=2011-04-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

